Course, there's nobody on the lake
to deliver to, so I get done a lot faster.

754
00:51:01,000 --> 00:51:02,831
(laughing)

755
00:51:02,920 --> 00:51:05,559
You've got a great setup here.
You're a lucky man.

756
00:51:05,640 --> 00:51:07,437
You're a lucky man, too.

757
00:51:09,080 --> 00:51:11,036
Yeah, I guess I am.

758
00:51:11,760 --> 00:51:13,716
Um... what uh...

759
00:51:14,080 --> 00:51:16,753
What do you usually do
at a time like this?

760
00:51:16,840 --> 00:51:19,434
Well, generally I just fall into the lake.

761
00:51:19,520 --> 00:51:21,351
Just uh...

762
00:51:21,440 --> 00:51:23,351
(Chelsea laughs)

763
00:51:23,440 --> 00:51:25,158
Whoa!

764
00:51:33,920 --> 00:51:37,674
All right, come on, Dad.
Big rolls here. You can beat him. Big rolls.

765
00:51:38,360 --> 00:51:40,316
Two threes. What does that mean?

766
00:51:40,400 --> 00:51:44,518
That means doubles,
which always means you get 14, you see?

767
00:51:44,640 --> 00:51:47,313
You send me home,
you get 20 more, for God's sake!

768
00:51:47,400 --> 00:51:49,960
- All right, Dadders!
- Good, huh?

769
00:51:50,040 --> 00:51:51,996
Excellent. You're a natural.

770
00:51:52,080 --> 00:51:54,594
I'm starting to regret
teaching you this game.

771
00:51:54,680 --> 00:51:57,319
Chels. Hey, Chels. Parcheesi pro.

772
00:51:57,400 --> 00:51:59,516
Chelsea doesn't like playing games.

773
00:51:59,600 --> 00:52:02,592
We don't know why.
Probably doesn't like losing.

774
00:52:02,680 --> 00:52:05,592
I tend to panic
when the competition gets too intense.

775
00:52:05,680 --> 00:52:08,069
- What's that supposed to mean?
- Nothing.

776
00:52:08,160 --> 00:52:10,549
We play serious Parcheesi around here.

777
00:52:10,640 --> 00:52:13,712
I let Norman win sometimes
just to keep his spirits up.

778
00:52:13,800 --> 00:52:14,755
Ha ha ha!

779
00:52:14,840 --> 00:52:18,310
What I'd like to know
is why you enjoy playing games.

780
00:52:18,400 --> 00:52:19,515
Huh?

781
00:52:19,600 --> 00:52:22,990
You seem to like beating people.
I wonder why.

782
00:52:29,640 --> 00:52:32,074
You got another chance, Bill.
Another roll.




